
** Backup Location

  - RMAN> configure channel 1 device type disk 
          format='/O2/tmp/rman/%d/%U' maxpiecesize 2g;

  - The format specifiers are described in the RMAN Reference

  - Note the directory '%d' must exist with upper letters. E.g.
    '/O2/tmp/rman/MANUAL'.

  - %d database name
  - %U uniuqe name

Back to OracleRman.
